creator: Fsj Games
descriptionHtml:
Step Master is a convinient pedometer that can track your daily steps, burned carolies and keep a healthy life.

Free to use
Step Master is completely free for you to count steps and start physical fitness anytime anywhere.

Easy to operate
The user interface is fresh and well-designed. There is only one button to start or pause counting steps. It is simple enougn to understand and operate easily.

Report and statistics
The daily, weekly and monthly reports about your walking steps will be intelligently generated into graphs, whilch can help you track your activity regularly.

Set your daily goal
If you want to lose weight or keep fit, the function of setting goal will help you.It can record your burned calories and encourage you to achieve your daily goal and get in better shape finally.

100% Privacy and security
No collection of your personal information. No GPS to locate your position. All your data is saved on your device only to ensure your privacy.You can use this step counter with confidence.

If you have any suggestions on Step Master, don't hesitate to let us know.

title: Step Master

creator: Fsj Games
descriptionHtml:
🤑Earn rewards
Step Master is a pedometer that allows you to earn money by walking and selling steps for money.
You just need to open it and walk, and then earn money by selling steps. You can also withdraw funds from your account, allowing you to enjoy a healthy life and earn money!

🏃‍♀️Report & Statistics
Daily, weekly and monthly reports of your steps will be intelligently generated in the form of graphs to help you keep track of your activity on a regular basis.
